  <div id="text-content_A49CBCB0-1E13-0135-862A-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can create account and sub-account level Question Banks in your Canvas instance. This allows anyone in the account to have access to the questions.</p><p><a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Video-Guide/Question-Banks-Admins/ta-p/383764" target="_blank">View a video about Question Banks.</a></p>
